Xopeng [Jawa]
Xopeng [Bahasa]
Xopeng [English]
Xopeng was born in Blitar, East Java. In a village called Jingglong, there are many rice fields and pets that become companions at dusk. The village is still thick with myths, multi-religious. Also a shaman. Xopeng was raised by village traditions with his students, as well as Surakarta, the City and the wilderness of the arts.
